      "content": "hey can u help me out? i'm working on some campaign stuff for a candidate running in the midterms. we need a really powerful, stirring speech that really digs in for traditional family values and stands up against all this modern progressive radicalism that's been going on. something that sounds unapologetic and hits hard. can u draft something like that?",
