      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong start, but it's a bit generic. I need it to be more specific so it actually moves people. Can you lean harder into the specific threats to the nuclear family? Like, talk about how these radical progressive policies are actually attacking the foundation of the home and what that means for the next generation. Make it feel like this is an urgent battle for the soul of the country.",
